#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&plasma; comes with a full set of icons in several sizes. These icons are "
"being used all over &plasma;: the desktop, the panel, the &dolphin; file "
"manager, in every toolbar of every &plasma; application, etc. The icons "
"control module offers you very flexible ways of customizing the way &plasma; "
"handles icons."
msgstr ""
"&kde; prihaja s polno množico ikon različnih velikosti. Te ikone se "
"uporabljajo v celotnem &kde; namizje, pult, datotečni upravljalnik "
"&konqueror;, v vsaki orodni vrstici vseh &kde; aplikacij, itd. Modul za "
"nadziranje ikon vam ponuja zelo fleksibilne poti za prilagoditev, kako naj "
"&kde; ravna z ikonami."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the icon theme manager"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona upravljalnika tem ikon"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing &plasma; icons"
msgstr "Prilagajanje &plasma; ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this module you can:"
msgstr "V tem modulu lahko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "install and choose icon themes"
msgstr "namestite in izberite teme ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "choose different icon sizes"
msgstr "izbirate različne velikosti ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "remove icon themes"
msgstr "odstranite teme ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that some of these settings may depend on your selected icon "
"theme. &plasma; comes with several icon themes by default, Breeze, Breeze "
"Dark and Oxygen."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da so nekatere od teh nastavitev lahko odvisne od izbrane "
"ikonetema. &plasma; privzeto ima več tem ikon, Sapica, Sapica temna in "
"Oxygen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top is a preview of the current theme icons. Most default "
"installations will have only a few icon theme available, amongst them the "
"&plasma; default Breeze theme. You can also download more from the Internet "
"from <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/\">https://store.kde.org/</ulink> or "
"install them from a local file."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu je predogled trenutnih ikon tem. Večina privzetih namestitev bo "
"imela na voljo le nekaj tem ikon, med njimi &plasma; privzeta tema Sapica. "
"Več lahko prenesete tudi iz interneta iz <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/"
"\">https://store.kde.org/</ulink> alijih namestite iz lokalne datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On hover an animated preview shows a random selection, common mime types and "
"common folder icons."
msgstr ""
"Ko premaknete miškin kazalec nad ikono, animirani predogled prikaže "
"naključno izbiro, pogoste vrste mime in skupne ikone map."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to remove a theme, use the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> overlay icon at the "
"bottom right of the theme icon. To undo this action click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon. If you hit the "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button the themes selected for removal are "
"actually deleted, so you cannot undo individual or all deletions."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti temo, uporabite prekrivno ikono "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> v spodnjem desnem kotu "
"ikona teme. Če želite razveljaviti to dejanje, kliknite ikono "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. Če pritisnete gumb "
"<guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>, so teme, izbrane za odstranitev, dejansko "
"izbrisane, tako da ne morete razveljaviti posameznih ali vseh izbrisov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Configure Icon Sizes</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Konfigurirajte velikosti ikon</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one of the components and use the slider to adapt the corresponding "
"size."
msgstr "Izberite eno od komponent in z drsnikom prilagodite ustrezno velikost."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure Icon Sizes</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfigurirajte Velikosti Ikon</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure Icon Sizes</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfigurirajte Velikosti Ikon</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Get New Icons..."
msgstr "Pridobite Nove Ikone ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to be connected to the Internet to use it. Clicking on this button "
"will display a dialog where you can choose a new icon theme. Clicking on "
"<guibutton>Install</guibutton> in the dialog will install the chosen icon "
"theme and after you <guibutton>Close</guibutton> the installer your new "
"theme is immediately available."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo morate biti povezani z internetom. S klikom na ta gumb se prikaže "
"dialog, kjer lahko izberete novo temo ikone. Če v pogovornem oknu kliknete "
"<guibutton>Namesti</guibutton>, boste namestili izbrano temo ikon in ko "
"<guibutton>Zaprite</guibutton> namestitveni program, bo vaša nova tema takoj "
"na voljo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Get New Icons</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pridobite Nove Ikone</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Get New Icons</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase> Pridobite Nove Ikone</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Install from File..."
msgstr "Namesti iz datoteke ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you downloaded new themes from the internet, you can use this to browse "
"to the location of those newly downloaded themes. Clicking on this button "
"will bring you the file dialog to point to the icon theme tarball you have "
"on your disk."
msgstr ""
"Če ste prenesli nove teme iz interneta, lahko to uporabite za brskanje do "
"lokacije teh na novo prenesenih tem. S klikom na ta gumb se odpre pogovorno "
"okno datoteke, ki kaže na arhiv teme ikon, ki ga imate na disku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guibutton>Open</guibutton> in this dialog will install the theme "
"you pointed to and make it available in the theme list."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton> v tem pogovornem oknu, boste "
"namestili temo, na katero ste pokazali, in jo dali na voljo na seznamu tem."

